sentences: On March 1, 2016, she suffered severe burn injuries on 80% of her body due to a fire in a cafe near the Wanda Plaza, Baoshan District, Shanghai, China.

It was later confirmed that she was covered in oil and set on fire; it is believed the perpetrator is a fan named "Miyamoto" a girl who is the leader of one of Tang AnQi's larger fanclubs, although no arrest has been made as of 14 September 2016.
As of April 2016, she is regularly undergoing surgeries and skin grafts.
